title: Enlightenment has no telltale physical/economic signature.
pid: e30efb25-c60e-4be0-b271-e9114c2e1f87
body: |2-
  It's usually not a monk on a mountain.
  It can be being late to a party.
  It can be fights with your teacher's children.
  It could be an egalitarian card game, where anyone can have the meaning.
